{"word":"G1018 - βραβεύω - brabeúō - brab-yoo'-o - Rule","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βραβεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">brabeúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">brab-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Rule</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆளு"},{"paragraph":"to decide, determine, to direct, control, rule"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G1017 - βραβεῖον - brabeîon - brab-i'-on/1017\">G1017</a>; to <i>arbitrate</i>, that is, (generally) to <i>govern</i> (figuratively <i>prevail</i>): - rule.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1018/1018\">G1018</a>, <a href=\"#/G1817/1817\">G1817</a>"}]}